The overall pavement width is reduced to 26 feet total or 13 feet per direction of travel. For wide load accommodations contact the project's Project Manager (Dusty Forsmann @ 509-751-1580 or 509-780-1244) or the project's Superintendent (Matt Uptmor @509-254-7966).
